---
const boundaries = [
  {
    label: 'acecore.net',
    body: 'Schools の紹介、SEO、無料体験 CTA を担当します。予約 DB、会員 session、Schools 決済は持ちません。',
  },
  {
    label: 'acecore-schools',
    body: '無料体験予約、会員ポータル、予約変更・キャンセル、read-only ICS、Schools 用 Stripe を担当します。',
  },
  {
    label: 'Acecore Accounts',
    body: '認証と共通 user id を担当します。予約や注文などの業務データは各 app 側に保持します。',
  },
]
---

<html lang="ja">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>Acecore Schools App</title>
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="Acecore Schools の予約、会員ポータル、外部カレンダー連携を担当するアプリケーションです。"
    />
  </head>
  <body>
    <main class="page-shell">
      <section class="intro" aria-labelledby="title">
        <p class="eyebrow">Acecore Schools</p>
        <h1 id="title">Schools app scaffold</h1>
        <p class="lead">
          この repo は Schools の予約、会員ポータル、外部カレンダー連携を
          acecore.net 本体から分離して実装するための土台です。
        </p>
        <div class="actions" aria-label="関連リンク">
          <a href="https://acecore.net/schools/">acecore.net Schools</a>
          <a href="/api/health">health check</a>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="boundary" aria-labelledby="boundary-title">
        <h2 id="boundary-title">Service boundary</h2>
        <div class="cards">
          {
            boundaries.map((item) => (
              <article>
                <h3>{item.label}</h3>
                <p>{item.body}</p>
              </article>
            ))
          }
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>

<style>
  :root {
    color-scheme: light;
    font-family:
      Inter, "Noto Sans JP", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
    background: #f6f7f2;
    color: #17201a;
  }

  * {
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }

  body {
    margin: 0;
    min-height: 100vh;
    background:
      linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(22, 101, 52, 0.08), transparent 34rem),
      linear-gradient(315deg, rgba(14, 116, 144, 0.1), transparent 30rem), #f6f7f2;
  }

  a {
    color: inherit;
  }

  .page-shell {
    width: min(1080px, calc(100% - 32px));
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 72px 0;
  }

  .intro {
    display: grid;
    gap: 20px;
    max-width: 760px;
    padding: 56px 0 48px;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    margin: 0;
    color: #0f766e;
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 0;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  h1,
  h2,
  h3,
  p {
    margin: 0;
  }

  h1 {
    max-width: 720px;
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 4.5vw, 5rem);
    line-height: 0.98;
    letter-spacing: 0;
  }

  .lead {
    max-width: 720px;
    color: #46554b;
    font-size: 1.08rem;
    line-height: 1.85;
  }

  .actions {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-top: 8px;
  }

  .actions a {
    min-height: 44px;
    border: 1px solid #b9c5bd;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 11px 16px;
    background: #ffffffcc;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .actions a:first-child {
    border-color: #14532d;
    background: #14532d;
    color: white;
  }

  .boundary {
    display: grid;
    gap: 20px;
    padding-top: 24px;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    letter-spacing: 0;
  }

  .cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 14px;
  }

  article {
    min-height: 180px;
    border: 1px solid #d5ddd6;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 22px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.78);
  }

  h3 {
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    color: #102c22;
    font-size: 1rem;
    letter-spacing: 0;
  }

  article p {
    color: #536057;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  @media (max-width: 760px) {
    .page-shell {
      width: min(100% - 24px, 1080px);
      padding: 36px 0;
    }

    .intro {
      padding: 36px 0 32px;
    }

    .cards {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>